{"tid":148443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警酒駕 撞電單車被捕","createTime":"2017-03-08T15:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T15:38:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a41aaf0f5263db15ff501cc28976d0e06727827","tid":148443,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"又有警務人員知法犯法！昨晚10時許，一輛電單車沿清風街天橋往維園道方向行駛，當駛至北角維園道近東區走廊時，因應前方交通情況停車，尾隨的私家車懷疑收掣不及撞上。39歲的電單車乘客腰部受傷，清醒送律敦治醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，發現50歲的私家車司機為休班警員，他未能通過酒精呼氣測試，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕，已獲准保釋候查，須於3月下旬向警方報到，案件交港島總區交通部意外調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"7d7bc976dd9205d11763de24888d1d937e137a45","tid":148443,"uid":89198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"今次又要捐幾多？"},{"pid":"666e64259a49cccb3400f13fb17b736a7031a2cc","tid":148443,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"阿蛇返工大壓力飲下酒有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快d出黎聲援"},{"pid":"c4b5f93961847ed60c69881566e5a5cb67c6aa0b","tid":148443,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次又要捐幾多？</blockquote><br />\n7個就打人就2000萬<br />\n以家出車喎，起碼千五個啦"},{"pid":"a30758b49e4a1e1f23cfbfaa71089c79d840677f","tid":148443,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}